description: This file is the entry point for a React-based frontend application. It imports React, ReactDOM, styles, and the main App component, then initializes and renders the React app within the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root to render React components into a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the specified React component hierarchy into the DOM.
